<%= "Congrats! #{@user.display_name} has invited #{@invitation.email} to join the '#{@invitation.league.name}' league (#{pluralize(@invitation.league.max_teams_per_user, 'entry')} max). " %>

<% if @invitation.league.elimination  %>
Your job, if you accept, is to pick a different <%= @invitation.league.season.season_type %> loser each week. That's it! Get one wrong, and you're done. The most correct picks wins.
<% else %>
Your job, if you accept, is to pick <%= @invitation.league.season.season_type %> losers each week. That's it! The most correct picks for the week wins.
<% end %>

League details:

Format: <%= @invitation.league.format %>
Commish: <%= @invitation.league.commish_names.join(', ') %>
<% if @invitation.league.elimination  %>
Starts: <%= @invitation.league.start_week.display %>
<% end %>

<% if @invitation.message && @invitation.message.length > 0  %>
A message was also included from <%= @user.display_name %>:

<%= @invitation.message %>

*****

<% end %>
To join the '<%= @invitation.league.name %>' league, follow this link and hit the 'Join' button:

<%= "https://www.loseorgohome.com/#/season/#{@invitation.league.season_id}/league/#{@invitation.league.id}" %>
